        <item>
            <title>政府将推动的士车队计划　强调不以的士牌价作为考量因素</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/14/%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e5%b0%87%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%95%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e8%bb%8a%e9%9a%8a%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83%e3%80%80%e5%bc%b7%e8%aa%bf%e4%b8%8d%e4%bb%a5%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e7%89%8c%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%9c%e7%82%ba/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e5%25b0%2587%25e6%258e%25a8%25e5%258b%2595%25e7%259a%2584%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e8%25bb%258a%25e9%259a%258a%25e8%25a8%2588%25e5%258a%2583%25e3%2580%2580%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e4%25b8%258d%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e7%259a%2584%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e7%2589%258c%25e5%2583%25b9%25e4%25bd%259c%25e7%2582%25ba</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/14/%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e5%b0%87%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%95%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e8%bb%8a%e9%9a%8a%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83%e3%80%80%e5%bc%b7%e8%aa%bf%e4%b8%8d%e4%bb%a5%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e7%89%8c%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%9c%e7%82%ba/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 06:00:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[网约车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250295</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col relative items-end"><div><div class="pt-0.5 juice:pt-0"><div class="gizmo-bot-avatar flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full juice:h-8 juice:w-8"><div class="relative p-1 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center bg-token-main-surface-primary text-token-text-primary h-8 w-8">运输及物流局局长林世雄在接受电台节目访问时，提及的士队伍牌照以及网约车规管方面的问题。他指政府已收到 15 份的士队伍牌照的申请，期望能在本月内批出不超过 5 个牌照，并在年底开始提供服务。林世雄强调，政府在研究网约车政策时，会以市民的整体利益为依归，不会考虑的士牌价的升跌。</div><div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex flex-grow flex-col max-w-full"><div class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex flex-col items-start whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 juice:w-full juice:items-end overflow-x-auto gap-2" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="952014e5-e4b2-453b-9a24-9c69b1579a96"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 juice:empty:hidden juice:first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"><p>林世雄指出，政府正进行相关的供求研究，希望能在 2025 年提出立法建议，以规管网约车平台。研究过程中，政府将广泛听取各方意见，确保在维持高效公共交通系统的同时，能满足市民对点对点交通服务的需求。</p><h3></h3><p>林世雄解释，的士车队的收费模式将有两种选择：按表收费并配以预约费，或点对点收费。而预约费将不设上限，政府相信市场会自行调节至合理水平。市民除了可以透过网上预约的方式使用的士车队服务外，亦可于街上直接截车，后者则只可按表收费。</p><p>他表示，当批出牌照后，车队需时间购买车辆、培训司机及建立平台，期望在今年年底有车队可以开始运作。当局对车队管理、司机质素、投诉管理、车龄、电子付款和车厢内安装摄录装置等方面都有严格要求，有信心能够提升乘客在预约和乘搭的士方面的体验。</p><h3></h3><p>林世雄表示，政府在规管网约车政策时，会考虑平衡的士行业和市民的利益，以市民的整体利益为首要考量。他指出，的士牌照价格由市场供求决定，并非政府研究网约车政策的考虑因素。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2010858/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%84%E8%BB%8A-%E6%9E%97%E4%B8%96%E9%9B%84-%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BB%A5%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%95%B4%E9%AB%94%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E7%82%BA%E5%85%88-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%89%8C%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%9C%A8%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%97">星岛日报</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1761510-20240714.htm?spTabChangeable=0">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=568085">NOW 新闻</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/hkgov-considering-regulateonline-car-hailing/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">港府研以发牌方式规管网约车平台　林世雄：不会偏帮的士业界</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/11/tada/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">零佣金网约车平台 TADA 进军香港，行政总裁：有信心脱颖而出</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/08/hk-rideshare-law-revise/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">政府建议发牌规管网约车平台　将进行可行性研究并咨询的士业界</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/14/%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e5%b0%87%e6%8e%a8%e5%8b%95%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e8%bb%8a%e9%9a%8a%e8%a8%88%e5%8a%83%e3%80%80%e5%bc%b7%e8%aa%bf%e4%b8%8d%e4%bb%a5%e7%9a%84%e5%a3%ab%e7%89%8c%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%9c%e7%82%ba/life-tech/">政府将推动的士车队计划　强调不以的士牌价作为考量因素</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
